{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_03_02",
  "title": "川咲さくら 2話 二人三脚で",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――元旦、午後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――New Year's Day‚ afternoon",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか生放送がある日に電車が止まるなんて……\nさくら達もそろそろ着くはずだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't believe the train stopped on the day of the live broadcast…\nSakura and the others should be arriving soon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1937538465,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2872.9128201999997,
          "startTime": 9.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 9.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません遅くなりました！\n遅刻してごめんなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so sorry!!\nI apologize for being late!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5115289465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 14.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "間に合ったか……\n遅刻は良くないが、無事で良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You made it in time…\nBeing late is not good‚ but I'm glad you're okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 20.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい……今日はいろんなことがあって\n良かったら後で話を聞いてもらってもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry… Today‚ various things happened‚ and…\nIf it's alright‚ can you listen to me later about what happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、詳しい話は後で聞くから\nとりあえずすぐリハーサルに参加してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ I'll hear the details later.\nFor now‚ please join the rehearsal immediately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 38.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\nそれじゃ、お仕事頑張って来ます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\nOkay then‚ I'll do my best with my work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3733.333333300003,
          "startTime": 42.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "やれやれ……大変な目にあったはずなのに\n今日もさくらは元気一杯だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… Despite going through a tough time‚\nSakura is full of energy today as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 50.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 50.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "……という訳で、朝早くに目が覚めちゃって\nみんなで初日の出を見に行くことになったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ I woke up early in the morning and\nwe decided to go see the first sunrise together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 58.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "初日の出を見に星見市へ行くと俺に連絡してくれたが\nその時は生放送までに帰れると思ってたんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You contacted me to go to Hoshimi City to see the first sunrise‚\nbut I thought you'd be back in time for the live broadcast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 66.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 70.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "まさか電車が止まるとは思わなくて……\nさとみさんが車で迎えに来てくれて助かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought the train would stop…\nLuckily‚ Satomi-san came to pick us up by car.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんって運転が上手だったんですね\n狭い道もすいすい走ってびっくりしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Satomi-san is really good at driving‚\nshe impressed me with how skillfully she drove through narrow roads.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 82.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはさとみさんの運転のこと\n知ってたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ did you already know\nabout Satomi-san's driving skills?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん\n運転が下手な人に大事なさくら達を預けたりしないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nI wouldn't entrust important people like you to someone who's a bad driver.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 92.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよね……さとみさんに連絡してくれて\nありがとうございます。おかげで無事に帰れました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Thank you for contacting Satomi-san.\nThanks to her‚ we made it back safely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それで、みんなで見た初日の出はどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ how was the first sunrise you all saw together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 105.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　朝焼けを見て気持ちが引き締まったというか\n初心を思い出して、今年も頑張ろうって思えました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was great! Watching the morning glow made me feel more determined\nand reminded me of my initial passion. I thought‚ \"Let's do our best again this year!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 114.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "その後は、みんなで神社へ初詣に行って\nおみくじを買ったり絵馬を描いたりしたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ we went to the shrine together for the first shrine visit of the year.\nWe bought omikuji （fortune slips） and wrote our wishes on ema （wooden votive plaques）.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 121.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんが素敵な晴れ着を見て目を輝かせたり\n雫ちゃんが可愛い巫女さん達を見て興奮したり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan was fascinated by the beautiful traditional clothes on display‚\nand Shizuku-chan got excited seeing the cute miko （shrine maiden） s.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.978641445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 130.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "とっても賑やかで楽しい初詣でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a lively and enjoyable shrine visit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 134.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "その後、みんなを私の家に招待しました\n前々から両親がみんなに会いたがっていたので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Afterward‚ I invited everyone to my house.\nMy parents had been wanting to meet them for a while…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "お母さんったら私が小さい頃のアルバムを出してきて\nみんなに見せるんですよ。凄く恥ずかしかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My mom even brought out my photo album\nfrom when I was little‚ and it was so embarrassing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 151
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "さくらが小さい頃の写真か。それは俺も見てみたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Photos from when Sakura was little‚ huh? I'd love to see them too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 157.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_02-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "やめて下さい！\n本当に恥ずかしかったんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ stop it!\nIt was really embarrassing‚ okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
